## Minimal custom waveNN example (Appendix-A style envelope)
##
## Play immediately from file start:
##   sbagenx -S examples/basics/prog-wave-custom-envelope-demo.sbg
##
## Render 2 minutes to WAV:
##   sbagenx -S -L 00:02 -W -o wave-demo.wav examples/basics/prog-wave-custom-envelope-demo.sbg

wave00: 0 0.2 1.0 0.2 0

ts-wave-demo: wave00:200+4/50

00:00 ts-wave-demo
